DATA VISUALIZATION

Numerical vs. Numerical
1. Scatterplot
2. Line plot
3. Heatmap for correlation
4. Joint plot

Categorical vs. Numerical
1. Bar chart
2. Violin plot
3. Categorical box plot
4.Swarm plot

Two Categorical Variables
1. Bar chart
2. Grouped bar chart
3. Point plot


